dct_title_s: Turan oder Türkistan zu C. Ritter's Erdkunde, Buch III, West Asien, Th. VII
dct_description_sm: Map of Central Asia; relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Tūrān is the ancient Iranian name for Central Asia; cf. Webster's new geographical dictionary.
dct_publisher_sm: Berlin : Verlag von D. Reimer, 1876 (Berlin : Lith. Anst. v. Leopold Kraatz)
